reviewText: This is the best classics I've been looking for years.

This rare tape is worth some money since the episodes are very hard to find now. Add to that the fact that if the older toons are release, they are subject to censorship, and we have a last chance to view these in their entirety. There are 5 Terrytoon Classics on this tape featuring the boys:
House Busters
Bulldozing the Bull
Blue Plate Symphony
Happy Landing
The Hitch Hikers
